22 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code Title 23, Chapter 110, Subchapter 1, is
23 amended to add an additional section to read as follows:
24 23-110-106. Prohibition — Definitions.
25 (a) As used in this section:
26 (1) "Casino licensee" means any individual, corporation,
27 partnership, association, trust, or other entity holding a license issued by
28 the Arkansas Racing Commission to conduct casino gaming at a casino; and
29 (2) "Franchise holder" means any individual, corporation,
30 partnership, association, trust, or other entity holding a franchise to
31 conduct horse racing under this chapter.
32 (b) A franchise holder or casino licensee is prohibited from:
33 (1) Accepting wagers on greyhound racing, either live or
34 simulcast; and
35 (2) Conducting greyhound racing.
